: : Rodimus Prime/Kup : :

The Maximal ships sensors pick up the Sweep assault force, signaling alarms.

Rodimus looks up, his mind still thinking of Nightlight&#39;s situation. Rodimus turns to face a monitor.

Rodimus: What on Cybertron is going on!

Kup is at the monitor in an instant, looking over the data.

Kup: Nightlight isnt our only problem now. This shows that a large force is entering Earths atmosphere. The trajectory shows them heading for the connon site. They...

Kup&#39;s optics grow wide, his mouth open as shock overtakes him.

Kup: Roddy, their configuraton match those of the Sweeps! I&#39;m not detecting any Decepticon signatures though.

Rodimus&#39; face grows serious. He stands behind Kup, looking over his shoulder. He studies the data for a moment.

Rodimus: Their Sweeps alright. Just like Scourge&#39;s goons back in the day. Not Decepticons thought. They must be Unicron&#39;s troops then. Remember he created the original Sweeps, along with Scourge, Cyclonus and Galvatron by reformatting Decepticons. Unicron must have learned of the connon project. The Minions he sent must have told him. Now he has ordered a massive strike on it to pave the way for his arrival.

Rodimus thinks over this dire situation for another few moments.

Rodimus Prime: This could be both bad a good for us. The good thing is that if Unicron feels that he must strike like this then the cannon must be capable of stopping him and hes scared. The bad thing is that its going to take one hell of a defensive effort to stop the Sweeps.

Rodimus looks to the Maximals and Autobot in the room.

Rodimus Prime: Kup, make an announcement. Round up the Maximals. I&#39;ll contact the other commanders.

Rodimus heads to a communciation station. Meanwhile Kup opens a commlink on all Maximal/Autobot channels.

Kup: Maximals this is Security Chief Kup. A serious situation has arised. Unicron has sent a massive force to strike at the cannon that is being constructed to defend against Unicron. All Maximals as well as other fections will be needed to defend it. Orders are here by issued to all Maximals and allies to report immedietly to the cannon construction site for battle. Good luck and may Primus watch over all of you. Kup out.

Kup closes the link.

Rodimus has set up repeating subspace visual/audio signal to be sent to the other faction commanders.

Rodimus Prime: This is Maximal Commander Rodimus Prime calling the Predacon and Tripredacus Commanders. We have detected a assault force arriving on the planet. This force is headed for the cannon. The force seems to consist of Sweeps, similar to the old Decepticon class. This leads us to believe that this force is a pre-emptive strike by Unicron. I&#39;m sending every bot that the Maximals have to defend the cannon. I suggest that the Predacons and Tripredacus do the same. I hope to see you on the battle field. Prime out.

Roddy closses that channel and faces the other bots in the room.

Rodimus Prime: Ok guys, its time. Transform and roll out!

Kup dashes through the halls, checking the ammo for his rifle on the way. Once outside he transforms to his truck mode and heads for the cannon.

Rodimus waits behind to make sure everyone follows their orders.

OOC: I&#39;m ready for a good ol&#39; fight!


